{"word":"ἀνάπαυσις","slug":"ἀνάπαυσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάπαυσις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναπαύω'><el>ἀναπαύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>repose, rest</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <i>relaxation, recreation</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>rest from</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}